&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[3].Y.F.Yue,H.Y.Fang,M.J.Wang,Z.Y.Wang,M.X.Yu*,Synthesis,characterisationandphotophysicalpropertiesofalpha,beta-diarylacrylonitrilederivatives,J.Chem.Res.,2009,6,337-380.
