&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[5].H.YFang,M.X.Yu*,Synthesisandphotophysicalpropertiesofnovelthiophenylacrylonitrilederivativescontainingatriphenylaminemoeity,J.Chem.Res.,2009,12,729-731.


